overview: Ashlynn, an incoming freshman, experiences firsthand the ups and downs of the college life. With a limo driver, a porn producer, trailer park bimbos, goth girls, professors, and a burger grillin' boyfriend, things are definitely about to get interesting, and with roommate, Margot, by her side, Ashlynn is opened up to an entirely new world full of sex, lies, and more sex!
tagline: She Just Wanted to Fit In...But She Never Expected This!
title: Ashlynn Goes to College
